A minimalistic illustration of two interlocking gears of different sizes suspended in empty space—one gear rendered in warm amber tones spinning clockwise, the other in cool teal spinning counterclockwise. Thin, elegant threads connect them, some taut and some gracefully looping, suggesting the flow of signals between asynchronous and synchronous worlds. The background is a clean gradient from soft cream to pale gray. Small geometric particles float around the connection points where the threads meet the gears, hinting at data in motion. The composition is balanced and airy, with generous negative space, conveying the elegant complexity of bridging two different operational paradigms.
